e dry on low heat or air dry. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightweight recycled polyester fabric for breathability and comfort. Slim fit for a close-to-body, performance-ready feel. Sleeveless design for enhanced airflow and freedom of movement. Dry Fit technology helps manage moisture during any athletic activity. True to size—recommended to order your usual size.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064630591642,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064630624410,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064630657178,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064630689946,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00805copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440872"}],"url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/collections\/drip-athletic.oembed","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}